reviews.text: True to size, comfortable to wear and keeps it's shape.

I love a good fitted T to wear under a blazer for work. This style feels so comfortable and soft to wear all day that I will purchase a few to keep in the work wardrobe rotation. I don’t like a clingy top at work, my personal preference and for me the style runs true to size. Ease of washing and ironing is important to me and I found this material easy to care for and has kept a nice bright white.

Wanted a non-see through t-shirt that doesn't loose its shape at the bottom. This tee delivered. Easily paired it with black jeans and a denim jacket for a casual look. Will be taking it with me on my upcoming holiday.
A perfect staple piece for mid season, fabulous  for layering and transitioning into the cooler months.
I bought this too for casual day wear. I have worn it tucked in and out and looks fantastic both ways
The first time a shirt hasn't been a good fit across the shoulders.
Basic white t-shirt. Nothing more,nothing less but better quality than most department stores and soft material.
I bought this basic white t shirt which you can dress down or place a jacket on top for a more formal look. The fabric wears well and stays in place
